144
00:12:48,314 --> 00:12:51,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>How will our opponent react to that?</i></b></font>

145
00:12:51,684 --> 00:12:55,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This second round will be turbulent...</i>
<i>Make no mistake!</i></b></font>

146
00:13:23,384 --> 00:13:27,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Give it a rest, old man. I already</i>
<i>know you've got good traction.</i></b></font>

147
00:13:27,714 --> 00:13:34,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, what gives? Is that all it's got,
that rotary rocket of yours?!</b></font>

148
00:13:37,264 --> 00:13:43,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I know from the first round that I lose</i>
<i>when coming out of corners on the hillclimb.</i></b></font>

149
00:13:43,104 --> 00:13:46,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No matter how much he rides me,</i>
<i>I just have to not let him pass.</i></b></font>

150
00:13:46,374 --> 00:13:50,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If I can keep outrunning him like this till</i>
<i>the turnaround point, this race is mine.</i></b></font>

151
00:13:50,374 --> 00:13:52,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I won't be beaten on the downhill!</i></b></font>

152
00:14:01,214 --> 00:14:03,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It looks like they've started a second round.</b></font>

153
00:14:03,424 --> 00:14:05,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Looks like it.</b></font>

154
00:14:05,024 --> 00:14:10,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure enough, I guess that lightweight FD
was pretty fast on the downhill.</b></font>

155
00:14:10,694 --> 00:14:13,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This will make things tough for Purple Shadow.</b></font>

156
00:14:13,534 --> 00:14:18,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're both big-framed cars, so pulling
ahead on the hillclimb will be hard.</b></font>

157
00:14:18,134 --> 00:14:22,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So Project D's strategy
will decide the race, eh?</b></font>

158
00:14:22,104 --> 00:14:25,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's a bright one, all right, Ryosuke Takahashi.</b></font>

159
00:14:25,774 --> 00:14:27,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still...</b></font>

160
00:14:27,874 --> 00:14:30,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Something bothers me.</b></font>

161
00:14:30,384 --> 00:14:31,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's that?</b></font>

162
00:14:31,884 --> 00:14:35,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke Takahashi is certainly a cunning foe...</b></font>

163
00:14:35,114 --> 00:14:42,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I don't think Kozo Hoshino could have
completely failed to see this coming.</b></font>

164
00:14:44,424 --> 00:14:49,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, it was Hoshino that
chose to lead in the first round.</b></font>

165
00:14:49,904 --> 00:14:55,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If he loses, then for a driver
called the "God Foot,"</b></font>

166
00:14:55,004 --> 00:14:57,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>wouldn't that be far too little planning?</b></font>

167
00:14:57,804 --> 00:14:59,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well...</b></font>

168
00:14:59,644 --> 00:15:07,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think Hoshino has some sort of
plan in mind. I can't help but feel that.</b></font>

169
00:15:09,684 --> 00:15:15,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If it's some sort of loophole in the rules...</i>
<i>then what on earth could it be?</i></b></font>

170
00:15:28,704 --> 00:15:30,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hyaa!</b></font>

171
00:15:37,144 --> 00:15:41,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Forget it. I don't know what</i>
<i>kind of power that thing packs,</i></b></font>

172
00:15:41,114 --> 00:15:43,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but there's absolutely no way</i>
<i>I'd let you pass me now!</i></b></font>

173
00:15:49,124 --> 00:15:53,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the shape of it, eh?
I've got the general picture.</b></font>

174
00:16:09,714 --> 00:16:13,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What is this? This mood like</i>
<i>people are expecting something...</i></b></font>

175
00:16:13,814 --> 00:16:17,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Gimme a break. There's no</i>
<i>reason anything'll happen.</i></b></font>

176
00:16:17,684 --> 00:16:20,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>As a racer with experience</i>
<i>at running mountain passes,</i></b></font>

177
00:16:20,924 --> 00:16:23,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can at least say that for sure!</i></b></font>

178
00:16:23,394 --> 00:16:27,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's no way he could pull</i>
<i>ahead on a course like this!</i></b></font>

179
00:16:27,264 --> 00:16:32,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Soon they'll be here at the turnaround</i>
<i>point, the yellow FD still in the lead.</i></b></font>

180
00:16:32,434 --> 00:16:36,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>They'll circle around this</i>
<i>pylon and head back down.</i></b></font>

181
00:16:36,174 --> 00:16:40,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>In that instant, Keisuke's</i>
<i>victory will be certain!</i></b></font>

182
00:16:57,364 --> 00:17:00,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The top is just ahead. We'll be up there soon.</i></b></font>

183
00:17:00,634 --> 00:17:03,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can do it. This race is mine!</i></b></font>

184
00:17:06,874 --> 00:17:09,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're here! There they are! They're comin' in!</b></font>

185
00:17:13,314 --> 00:17:14,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay!</b></font>

186
00:17:30,824 --> 00:17:33,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're comin' in side-by-side!</b></font>

187
00:17:34,064 --> 00:17:35,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What are you doing?!</i></b></font>

188
00:18:06,434 --> 00:18:09,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hoshino's out in front!</b></font>

189
00:18:09,334 --> 00:18:12,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It can't be. Don't tell me...</b></font>

190
00:18:12,364 --> 00:18:17,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He was waiting for the instant when
the turn toward the downhill begins?!</b></font>

191
00:18:17,144 --> 00:18:23,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a crazy thing to do! That GT-R
came charging in without hesitation.</b></font>

192
00:18:23,814 --> 00:18:27,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If Keisuke hadn't moved, it would've
been a terrible head-on crash!</b></font>

193
00:18:27,984 --> 00:18:30,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Screw you! You'd do something like this?!</b></font>

194
00:18:30,554 --> 00:18:34,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No, that's not right. They may</i>
<i>have looked about the same,</i></b></font>

195
00:18:34,894 --> 00:18:40,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but our opponent entered the spin</i>
<i>turn a split-second earlier.</i></b></font>

196
00:18:40,634 --> 00:18:44,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's where the lead</i>
<i>position was taken from us.</i></b></font>

197
00:18:47,004 --> 00:18:51,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I timed it so we'd be side-by-side</i>
<i>when we came out of the corner.</i></b></font>

198
00:18:51,004 --> 00:18:54,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That was quite satisfactory, if I say so myself.</i></b></font>

199
00:18:54,514 --> 00:18:58,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He got me. Now all I can do is overtake him!</i></b></font>

200
00:18:58,344 --> 00:19:02,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It looks like Keisuke had the tables
turned on him at the turnaround point.</b></font>

201
00:19:02,924 --> 00:19:07,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As I thought. Sure enough,
he did not pass up his opportunity.</b></font>

202
00:19:07,254 --> 00:19:10,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This puts us at an overwhelming disadvantage.</b></font>

203
00:19:10,524 --> 00:19:16,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All we can do now is bet on Keisuke's
natural ability to spring into action.</b></font>

204
00:19:16,104 --> 00:19:18,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The rougher and more
heated this race becomes,</b></font>

205
00:19:18,764 --> 00:19:20,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the higher the probability.</b></font>

206
00:19:20,704 --> 00:19:23,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The more turbulent this is,
the greater our chances.</b></font>

207
00:19:25,704 --> 00:19:31,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The one thing that worries</i>
<i>me is Ko falling silent.</i></b></font>

208
00:19:31,714 --> 00:19:34,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't get too heated.</i></b></font>

209
00:19:47,064 --> 00:19:50,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Drifting, huh? If that's how you want to play it...</i></b></font>

210
00:19:54,304 --> 00:19:55,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

211
00:19:57,104 --> 00:19:59,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hoshino pulled ahead at the turnaround point!</b></font>

212
00:19:59,144 --> 00:20:01,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah!</b></font>

213
00:20:01,314 --> 00:20:02,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I knew there was no way he'd lose!</b></font>

214
00:20:02,814 --> 00:20:06,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh. So that was Hoshino's plan?</b></font>

215
00:20:06,814 --> 00:20:08,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There they are!</b></font>

216
00:20:10,484 --> 00:20:12,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Drift vs. drift?!</b></font>

217
00:20:12,424 --> 00:20:14,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The GT-R is a 4WD, right?!</b></font>

218
00:20:14,554 --> 00:20:16,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This thing's gettin' more and more heated!</b></font>

219
00:20:16,724 --> 00:20:19,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's goin' on with Hoshino?</b></font>

220
00:20:19,094 --> 00:20:21,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What on earth is going on?</b></font>

221
00:20:21,594 --> 00:20:26,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It could be that this is
according to Hoshino's plan.</b></font>

222
00:20:26,504 --> 00:20:28,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Without a doubt, his tires have lost their grip,</b></font>

223
00:20:28,434 --> 00:20:33,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>making it easier to understeer
on downhill corners.</b></font>

224
00:20:33,344 --> 00:20:35,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If he fishtailed the rear section at corner entry,</b></font>

225
00:20:35,774 --> 00:20:38,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he could control the front-end push.</b></font>

226
00:20:38,644 --> 00:20:43,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At first glance it appears utterly reckless,
but there's sound reasoning behind it.</b></font>

227
00:20:43,754 --> 00:20:45,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Also...</b></font>

228
00:20:45,024 --> 00:20:50,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If the GT-R drifts its big rear section
on already narrow streets,</b></font>

229
00:20:50,324 --> 00:20:54,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it takes up that much more space,
effectively blocking the way...</b></font>

230
00:20:54,594 --> 00:20:58,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...creating a barricade that
stretches the width of the road.</b></font>

231
00:21:08,474 --> 00:21:11,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I hadn't planned on gettin' so flashy,</i></b></font>

232
00:21:11,384 --> 00:21:15,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but if my opponent is gonna take</i>
<i>things this far, I can't back down now!</i></b></font>

233
00:21:15,554 --> 00:21:19,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is a different world, beyond reason.</i></b></font>

234
00:21:19,124 --> 00:21:21,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And I won't let anyone criticize!</i></b></font>

235
00:21:22,894 --> 00:21:28,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just don't understand it.
Mr. Joshima, they're drifting.</b></font>

236
00:21:28,364 --> 00:21:32,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Both Mr. Hoshino's GT-R and the pursuing FD...</b></font>

237
00:21:32,034 --> 00:21:37,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Isn't the sensible thing to do to race
with a little more care for their tires?</b></font>

238
00:21:37,744 --> 00:21:43,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, sometimes the only ones who
understand are the people holding the wheel.</b></font>

239
00:21:43,084 --> 00:21:46,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure enough, they're cut from the same cloth.</b></font>

240
00:21:46,314 --> 00:21:51,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess we just keep quiet and watch these
two fools engage in their battle of wills.</b></font>

241
00:21:51,884 --> 00:21:56,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're both up on the main stage now...</b></font>

242
00:21:56,524 --> 00:22:02,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There is a logical reason for
Kozo Hoshino's repeated use of drift.</b></font>

243
00:22:02,034 --> 00:22:06,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>However, there is no such
reason supporting Keisuke's.</b></font>

244
00:22:06,734 --> 00:22:10,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Put simply, it is the willfulness of one
who drives a rear-wheel vehicle.</b></font>

245
00:22:10,244 --> 00:22:14,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke has responded with
competitive spirit rather than reasoning...</b></font>

246
00:22:14,844 --> 00:22:17,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fight drift with drift.</b></font>

247
00:22:17,684 --> 00:22:21,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There is one aspect in which Kozo Hoshino
and Keisuke closely resemble each other.</b></font>

248
00:22:21,714 --> 00:22:24,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke's actions make
no disguise of his feelings,</b></font>

249
00:22:24,184 --> 00:22:27,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>which in this case fuels
Hoshino's fighting spirit.</b></font>

250
00:22:27,894 --> 00:22:31,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That is what suddenly made
this a battle of drifting.</b></font>

251
00:22:45,704 --> 00:22:47,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My tires!</i></b></font>

252
00:22:50,084 --> 00:22:52,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ko is probably enjoying this</i>
<i>more than he can stand.</i></b></font>

253
00:22:52,544 --> 00:22:56,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But Ko, this turn of events</i>
<i>will count more against</i></b></font>

254
00:22:56,884 --> 00:22:59,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>the GT-R, with its heavy frame.</i></b></font>

255
00:22:59,724 --> 00:23:02,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Drawing this out would be</i>
<i>disadvantageous in terms of tires...</i></b></font>

256
00:23:02,994 --> 00:23:05,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He should've known that from the start.</i></b></font>

257
00:23:05,724 --> 00:23:11,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>They're not too far off now. I'm sure</i>
<i>Keisuke has no intention of quitting.</i></b></font>

258
00:23:11,434 --> 00:23:15,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We still don't know what will happen</i>
<i>until that goal line is crossed!</i></b></font>

259
00:23:24,814 --> 00:23:28,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Dammit! It's overshooting all on its own!</i></b></font>

260
00:24:53,504 --> 00:24:55,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--All right!
--Yes!</b></font>

261
00:25:21,194 --> 00:25:25,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A rose that's bloomed on the battlefield,</i>
<i>for the reason they don't know</i></b></font>

262
00:25:25,204 --> 00:25:29,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A caterpillar that can only move forward</i>
<i>tramples it under foot again today</i></b></font>

263
00:25:29,074 --> 00:25:33,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yo, hates and pain, increasing only hatred</i></b></font>

264
00:25:33,374 --> 00:25:37,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hates and pain, with those</i>
<i>social conditions transmitted live</i></b></font>

265
00:25:37,484 --> 00:25:46,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hold me with stronger hands</i></b></font>

266
00:25:46,224 --> 00:25:52,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Your voice in a restless night</i>
<i>(For the reason they don't know)</i></b></font>

267
00:25:52,394 --> 00:25:58,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The world will someday be shedding blood</i>
<i>(All around the world)</i></b></font>

268
00:25:58,464 --> 00:26:08,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let me forget that kind of news,</i>
<i>I don't want to understand</i></b></font>

269
00:26:09,584 --> 00:26:16,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nobody reason, nobody sure where is the end</i></b></font>

270
00:26:16,624 --> 00:26:25,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ah, sing gently just a little more, even if it's a lie</i></b></font>

271
00:26:25,164 --> 00:26:29,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Check it, conflicting information is</i>
<i>already reported by the mass media</i></b></font>

272
00:26:29,164 --> 00:26:33,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The outnumbered convey the</i>
<i>deep fears of the whole situation</i></b></font>

273
00:26:33,204 --> 00:26:37,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Reason is flammable, an age</i>
<i>lacking the power of restraint, yeah</i></b></font>

274
00:26:37,204 --> 00:26:41,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Devoting yourself body and spirit,</i>
<i>you keep receiving that baptism</i></b></font>

275
00:26:41,514 --> 00:26:48,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nobody reason, nobody sure where is the end</i></b></font>

276
00:26:48,514 --> 00:26:57,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If rowing a boat that's untrustworthy</i>
<i>and on the verge of breaking...</i></b></font>

277
00:26:57,464 --> 00:27:04,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nobody reason, no one</i>
<i>confess that it was wrong</i></b></font>

278
00:27:04,534 --> 00:27:14,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ah, sing gently just a little more, even if it's a lie</i></b></font>

